Usage: set_resistance [-help] <resistance_value> <net_list> [-max] [-min]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<resistance_value>     # Specifies the value for the wire resistance
                       # (float, required)
<net_list>             # Specifies a list of nets on which the wire resistance
                       # is set (string, required)
-max                   # Specifies that the asserted resistance is the maximum
                       # resistance (bool, optional)
-min                   # Specifies that the asserted resistance is the minimum
                       # resistance (bool, optional)